element.name: Glenmacnass View by Fjon, Traditional Cache (1.5/2.5)
element.description: Nearly a cache and dash with nice views.
element.long-description: A steep scramble up a hill to a spot with a nice view. There is car parking very close by, but the cache is straight up, so you should be wearing sensible shoes, and be careful up there - note the terrain rating.
